verbs.description: Yet another interesting development in the Mueller investigation . The FBI [V: has] been given wiretapped conversations involving Alexander Torshin , one of the highest - ranking banking officials in Russia and a key Putin ally , recorded by the Spanish government . Torshin met with Donald Trump , Jr. several times and is also the man most responsible for getting Russian backing …
